Subject: Re: [VB] want less steering play

Replace the center pin and bushings with a new kit.  Ronnie at Oldvolks
sells them.  If there is play in the drag link, get a new one and
replace the other tie rod end or entire thing if need be.  I'd do the
dampner last.  It has very little to do with excess play.

http://www.vintagebus.com/howto/pivot.html

Read...do.  

Steve


